name: Cubeparty.GitHub.io
body:
### Welcome to Liaison Cube Party
This repository provides invitation to Liaison Cube Party 2015. Invitation will also provide simple framework to [three.js](http://threejs.org/) library that can be used as template for production. Other excellent source is [three.js examples](http://threejs.org/examples/).

### Cube Party 2015 date && venue
Date and time will be announced later. Venue is Liaison Tampere Office.

### Cube Party 2015 competition rules
tbd

### Support or Contact
You can use these this repository's issue tracker to ask technical question or send email.
